lenders.name: Admin
lenders.occupational_info:
PLEASE READ THE FOLLOWING!
Dear Sir or Madam,

 We are a family run British finance packaging company based in Spain. I personally have been in the finance industry for over 40 years. We put the whole deal together to put on the lenders table which includes searches using Equifax or Experian or Dunn & Bradstreet. 

We do unfortunately charge a processing fee. This is to cover out out of pocket expenses such as searches & phone calls etc, For residential it is €385.00 and for commercial it is €465.00 and at close we want a maximum of 1%. However prior to you paying anything, you will receive an in principle offer from us, once you receive this it means a lender has accepted your file with a view to lending.

If the lender requires an application fee, we will add this also. In relation to valuations and/or appraisals and/or site visits these amounts will be requested at a later date but will be documented in the in principle offer as we do not like giving clients sudden shocks! But prior to paying any of these you will have a firm commitment stating that the funds are available subject to valuation and or appraisal and or a site visit.

On an in principle offer, everything is documented, including all of the initial costs you will have to pay, the amount of finance offered, the interest rate, the total monthly repayments, the total interest that you will be paying, everything that you need in to decide if you wish to proceed or not. The in principle offer has a five day life span on it, and to proceed you must sign and return it to us within this time frame with your payment.  

We do good business with real lenders worldwide and have the following deals available. We work on the principle that if a client is happy they will spread our name around, so we don’t have a website. But we get a sufficient number of clients to keep us going.

FOR RESIDENTIAL
FIRST TIME BUYERS, PURCHASE, REMORTGAGES, EQUITY RELEASE, BUY LET, HOLIDAY HOMES, BRIDGING FINANCE, LAND ACQUISITION, SELF BUILD, RENOVATION, IMPROVEMENTS, PRIVATE MARINE, PRIVATE AIRCRAFT, SEMI COMMERCIAL & START UP. 
FOR COMMERCIAL
COMMERCIAL, CORPORATE, BRIDGING FINANCE, LAND ACQUISITION, RENOVATION, IMPROVEMENTS, DEVELOPMENT CONSTRUCTION, INFRASTRUCTURE, FACTORING, SHIPPING, AIRCRAFT, EXPANSION, HOTELS, MOTELS, CASINOS, COUNTRY CLUBS, GOLF COURSES, OFFICES, POWER STATIONS, OIL REFINERIES, COMPLEXES, RESORTS, VENTURE CAPITAL, LETTERS OF CREDIT, BANK GUARANTEES & INSURANCE GUARANTEES.

The facilities we have available are as follows: ALL SUBJECT TO STATUS, ALL ASSET BASED FINANCING (SECURED AGAINST AN ACCEPTABLE ASSET)

UP TO 100% LOAN TO VALUE (FSV), 5 TO 30 YEAR TERMS AVAILABLE, APPLICANTS FROM 18 TO 80 ACCEPTED, NO UPPER LIMIT OF FUNDING, CURRENCIES AVAILABLE׃ EUROS €, POUNDS STERLING £ & US DOLLARS $.

I have been as informative as I possibly can with this letter, but if you have and further questions then please do not hesitate to ask them and we hope you consider us for your funding.

Respectfully Yours

Email: infoatatoz@gmail.com Telephone: (0034) 677823872
